data.description:
This project includes all *official* **React-Bootstrap Components** with original options sets.

Also includes:
* React JS component source code generator
* React JS component + Reflux actions source code generator
* Quick notes for all React-Bootstrap components

#### Description This project was developed for real-life site on http://helmetrex.com
Additionaly this project serves as an example of what you can do in Structor. Here you can find a lot of technologies which will help to develop a Web application for Node JS using React library.
Such as: * Set of components: react-bootstrap * Flux implementation: redux, redux-thunk, react-redux * Routing: react-router **Remember, using Structor you don't have to install additionally all hot-reloading infrastructure (webpack-dev-middleware, webpack-hot-reloading, react-transform-hmr) because all these are embedded into the builder.** Read more about structure of the project's source code in detailed overview.

Includes: 

- React Bootstrap components (2.5.0)
- webpack configuration
- Components with validation, feedback, and etc.
